  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK844">
<l>veṇmai yeṉappaṭuva tiyāteṉi ṉoṇmai</l>
<l>yuṭaiyamyā meṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is called want of wisdom is the vanity which says, "We are wise".</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
